        <div class="dashed_divider m-b-30"></div>
        <p class="blue_bg_para m-b-30">The core purpose of the Shiv Yog foundation can be summed in this Sanskrit saying, “Loka Samastha Sukhino Bhavantu” which is a prayer and an intention for all living beings to find peace and tranquility.</p>

        <div class="heading_subtitle core-values-title">Core Values</div>
        <div class="dashed_divider m-b-30"></div>
        <div class="event_listing">
          <div class="event_title"><em>Never complain but create.</em></div>
        </div>

        <div class="event_listing">
          <div class="event_title"><em>"Vasudhaiva Kutumbakam" – the whole world is one big family!</em></div>
        </div>

        <div class="event_listing">
          <div class="event_title"><em>Every person can be the creator of his own destiny, if he so chooses.</em></div>
        </div>

        <div class="event_listing">
          <div class="event_title"><em>Love everyone, Forgive everyone and Accept everyone unconditionally.</em></div>
        </div>

        <div class="event_listing">
          <div class="event_title"><em>We own 100% responsibility for everything that happens in our lives.</em></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="clear"></div>

<section id="what_is_shivyog">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <div class="heading_subtitle">Vision</div>
        <div class="dashed_divider"></div>
        <div class="heading_title">Happy, Healthy, peaceful world</div>
